These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, scientific
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, ritmeester
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | drama |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | swisher    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, metal
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the fan of soul##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Music-Genre      | metal  | soul   |
| Birthday   | may | august  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: spinach, apricot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, metal
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming
1. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Food         | spinach   | apricot  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | punk  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey   | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, writing
2 different pets are kept: dog, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Hobby          | camping | writing |
| Pet   | mouse   | dog   |
| Transport     | train       | ship      |

