.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: country, techno
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, white
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
3. the fan of country is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre    | techno | country     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Color   | white | ivory    |

