.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
City: hannover, san-francisco
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, chestnut
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| City         | san-francisco | hannover |
| Color   | blood-red     | chestnut     |
| Pet           | pony          | lizard     |

